02.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-3-1745848330-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-423644%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Emahua%20kala%20jamun%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Emaas%20ke%20soole%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20loved%20for%20the%20decadence%20they%20bring%20to%20the%20menu%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChef%20Amninder%20virtually%20points%20us%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ewadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20experience%20(a%20%3Cem%3Ewadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20traditional%20farm%20or%20orchard%20common%20in%20Maharashtra).%20The%20kitchen%20garden%2C%20she%20explains%2C%20is%20a%20Mediterranean%20experience%20around%20a%20wood-fired%20oven.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20guests%20arrive%2C%20we%20offer%20them%20a%20glass%20of%20sparkling%20wine%20and%20some%20canap%C3%A9s.%20They%20can%20make%20their%20own%20pizzas%20here%20and%20enjoy%20these%20at%20a%20community%20table%20where%20they%20are%20surrounded%20by%20pumpkin%20creepers.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20seem%20unbelievable%20that%20the%20land%20is%20home%20to%20a%20major%20portion%20of%20the%20ingredients%20that%20go%20into%20the%20food.%20A%20mini-universe%20of%20self-sufficiency%2C%20you%20could%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98If%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20find%20the%20ingredient%2C%20grow%20it%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Assam%2C%20the%20paucity%20of%20available%20ingredients%20compelled%20chef%20Amninder%E2%80%99s%20mother%20to%20grow%20what%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20in%20the%20markets.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20always%20trying%20to%20up%20her%20game%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chef%20states%2C%20backtracking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366063%2Fnehal-shah-travel-